comment: Nowitzki (DAL) sets the screen on Williams (LAL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Clarkson (LAL) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Williams' (DAL) driving layup attempt.
RHH shows that Nowtizki (DAL) makes incidental contact with Clarkson's (LAL) arm that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Williams (LAL) maintains legal guarding position and cleanly blocks Barea's (DAL) driving layup attempt.
Clarkson (LAL) and Williams (DAL) make incidental contact with one another during rebounding.
Young (LAL) releases his dribble prior to moving his pivot foot.

R-Slash shows that Barea (DAL) clamps and pulls Williams' (LAL) arm on the drive, and then falls back from him. The trail official incorrectly makes the offensive call on Williams because he only sees Barea's histrionics, not the clamp.
Matthews (DAL) sets the screen on Randle (LAL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Young (LAL) makes incidental contact with Nowitzki (DAL) that does not affect his FOM on the cut away from the ball.
Powell (DAL) makes incidental contact with Randle (LAL) that does not affect his RSBQ.
